WARFRAMEMOD-AEGIS_STORM.description:
Remove all [gold]Shield[/gold] of yours.
For every 1 [gold]Shield[/gold] removed, deal {ExtraDamage:diff()} damage to all enemies.{InCombat:
(Deal {CalculatedDamage:diff()} damage)|}

WARFRAMEMOD-PENANCE.description:
Remove all [gold]Shield[/gold] of yours.
For every {TotalShield:diff()} [gold]Shield[/gold] removed, draw 1 card.{InCombat:
(Draw {Cards:diff()} {Cards:plural:card|cards})|}

WARFRAMEMOD-THURIBLE.description:
Lose {energyPrefix:energyIcons(1)} at the start of each turn, until you draw a [gold]Thurible[/gold] again.
When you draw this card, gain {Energy:energyIcons()} for each {energyPrefix:energyIcons(1)} lost caused by a [gold]Thurible[/gold].{InCombat:
(Gain {TotalEnergy:energyIcons()})|}

WARFRAMEMOD-VIRULENCE.description:
Deal {Damage:diff()} damage, gain {Energy:energyIcons()}.
Every {Requirement:diff()} times you play this card, permanently double this card's damage.{InCombat:
(Play {Countdown:diff()} more {Countdown:plural:time|times} to increase its damage.)|}
